Getting and building it:
------------------------

		git clone git@github.com:epronk/python-blog.git
		git clone git@github.com:epronk/python-blog-content.git


To bootstrap the environment.
-----------------------------

This creates a virtual env.
Installs make and markdown2.

		cd python-blog-content
		./bootstrap


Build the content
-----------------

		make compile


Deploy the content to the ISP
-----------------------------

		make deploy
